signature: <I, O> Iterator<O> transformedIterator(Iterator<? extends I> iterator, Transformer<? super I, ? extends O> transformer)

enhanced_by.reason: Environment setup is required before transforming iterators to ensure proper initialization of resources.
Transformers need to be initialized before they can be used in the transformation process.
Verifying the transformation results ensures that the transformed iterator behaves as expected.
Comparing the transformed iterator with the original iterator can help validate the transformation process.
